# AutoRev Brand Guidelines

> **CRITICAL:** ALL UI code must use these brand colors and typography. Non-compliance results in inconsistent user experience.

---

## Part 1: Core Brand Colors

### 1.1 Color Constants

```css
/* Background Colors */
--brand-bg-primary: #0d1b2a;     /* Main page backgrounds */
--brand-bg-secondary: #1b263b;   /* Cards, elevated surfaces */
--brand-bg-card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
--brand-bg-card-hover: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);

/* Text Colors */
--brand-text-primary: #ffffff;
--brand-text-secondary: #94a3b8;   /* Slate-400 - Secondary text */
--brand-text-tertiary: #64748b;    /* Slate-500 - Tertiary text */
--brand-text-muted: #475569;       /* Slate-600 - Muted text */

/* Accent Colors - SEMANTIC MEANINGS */
--brand-lime: #d4ff00;             /* EMPHASIS: Headlines, CTAs, badges */
--brand-teal: #10b981;             /* IMPROVEMENTS: Gains, selections, positive */
--brand-blue: #3b82f6;             /* BASELINE: Stock values, original data */
--brand-gold: #d4a84b;             /* LABELS: Brand accent, category labels */
```

### 1.2 Color Usage Rules

| Color | Hex | USE FOR | NEVER USE FOR |
|-------|-----|---------|---------------|
| **Lime** | `#d4ff00` | Primary CTAs, emphasized headlines, badges | Body text, backgrounds |
| **Teal** | `#10b981` | Improvements, gains, active selections, positive changes | Static labels, warnings |
| **Blue** | `#3b82f6` | Baseline/stock values, original specs, comparison data | Success states, CTAs |
| **Gold** | `#d4a84b` | Category labels, brand accent on dark, secondary buttons | Primary CTAs, improvements |

