## Part 3: Typography

### 3.1 Font Families

```css
--font-display: var(--font-oswald, 'Oswald'), sans-serif;  /* Headers */
--font-body: var(--font-inter, 'Inter'), sans-serif;       /* Body text */
--font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', monospace;       /* Data/stats */
```

### 3.2 Type Scale (Mobile-First)

| Name | Mobile | Desktop | Usage |
|------|--------|---------|-------|
| Hero | 28px | 56px | Page headlines |
| H1 | 26px | 48px | Section titles |
| H2 | 22px | 36px | Card headers |
| H3 | 18px | 28px | Subsections |
| Base | 13px | 16px | Body text |
| Small | 11px | 14px | Labels |
| XS | 10px | 12px | Fine print |

### 3.3 Data/Stat Typography

**Hero Stats (544 HP, 558 LB-FT, etc.):**

```css
.stat-value-hero {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 24px;  /* MOBILE OPTIMIZED */
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85) 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}
```

**Improvement Values:**

```css
.stat-improved {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #10b981;  /* Teal */
}
```

**Baseline Values:**

```css
.stat-baseline {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #3b82f6;  /* Blue */
}
```

### 3.4 Labels

```css
/* Uppercase category labels */
.label-uppercase {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #d4a84b;  /* Gold */
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
}
```

