## Part 4: Button Patterns

### 4.1 Primary CTA (Lime)

```css
.btn-primary {
  background: #d4ff00;
  color: #0a1628;  /* Navy */
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 16px 32px;
  border-radius: 100px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
  background: #bfe600;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(212, 255, 0, 0.3);
}
```

### 4.2 Secondary Button (Outline)

```css
.btn-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  padding: 16px 32px;
  border-radius: 100px;
}

.btn-secondary:hover {
  border-color: #d4ff00;
  color: #d4ff00;
}
```

### 4.3 Accent Button (Gold) - Secondary Actions

```css
.btn-accent {
  background: #d4a84b;
  color: #000;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  border-radius: 10px;
}
```

