## Part 6: Pre-Flight Checklist

Before submitting ANY UI code, verify:

| Check | Question |
|-------|----------|
| ☐ Background | Using `#0d1b2a` (not pure black)? |
| ☐ Primary CTA | Using lime `#d4ff00` (not gold/orange)? |
| ☐ Improvements | Using teal `#10b981` for gains? |
| ☐ Baseline | Using blue `#3b82f6` for stock values? |
| ☐ Stats | Using monospace font for numeric data? |
| ☐ Hero Stats | Using 24px size with metallic gradient? |
| ☐ Labels | Using gold `#d4a84b` for category labels? |
| ☐ Secondary Text | Using `#94a3b8` (not gray-400)? |

